{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_2786aed32ffe2LKopNEVo1fXh6","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d87a23495001ZZkdWKreuMmK6l","parts":[{"id":"prt_d87a23d01001ns45H2Gx71S1Ms","messageID":"msg_d87a23495001ZZkdWKreuMmK6l","sessionID":"ses_2786aed32ffe2LKopNEVo1fXh6","type":"text","text":"## 仓库配置总结\n\n### 环境配置完成\n\n**Python 环境:**\n- Python 3.11.2\n- 虚拟环境：`/workspace/venv`\n\n**关键依赖版本:**\n- featuretools: 1.31.0 (editable install from /workspace)\n- pandas: 2.3.3 (降级自 3.0.2，解决 woodwork 兼容性问题)\n- numpy: 1.26.4\n- scipy: 1.17.1\n- woodwork: 0.30.0 (降级自 0.31.0，解决 API 兼容性问题)\n- dask: 2026.3.0\n- distributed: 2026.3.0\n\n### 关键改动\n\n1. **安装 python3-pip 和 python3.11-venv** - 用于创建虚拟环境\n2. **创建虚拟环境** - `/workspace/venv`\n3. **安装依赖** - `pip install -e \".[test]\"`\n4. **降级 pandas** - 从 3.0.2 降级到 2.3.3 (woodwork 与 pandas 3.x 不兼容)\n5. **降级 woodwork** - 从 0.31.0 降级到 0.30.0 (解决 API 变更问题)\n6. **安装 graphviz** - 用于 plotting 测试\n7. **安装 dask** - 用于并行计算测试\n\n### 验证测试结果\n\n**通过的测试:**\n- ✅ `featuretools/tests/test_version.py` (1 个测试)\n- ✅ `featuretools/tests/demo_tests/` (4 个测试)\n- ✅ `featuretools/tests/config_tests/` (3 个测试)\n- ✅ `featuretools/tests/utils_tests/` (40 个测试)\n- ✅ `featuretools/tests/entityset_tests/` (137 个测试，除 plotting 外)\n- ✅ `featuretools/tests/entityset_tests/test_plotting.py` (6 个测试)\n- ✅ `featuretools/tests/synthesis/` (124 个测试)\n- ✅ `featuretools/tests/computational_backend/` (106 个测试)\n- ✅ 基本 DFS 功能验证\n\n**失败的测试:**\n- ❌ `featuretools/tests/primitive_tests/transform_primitive_tests/test_savgol_filter.py::TestSavgolFilter::test_nans` \n  - **失败原因**: scipy 的 `savgol_filter` 函数与新版 numpy 的 `asarray_chkfinite` 不兼容（numpy 版本问题，非 featuretools 代码问题）\n\n### 最终状态\n\n✅ **仓库配置成功**\n\nfeaturetools 1.31.0 已成功安装并验证。核心功能（EntitySet 创建、DFS 特征生成、计算后端等）均正常工作。唯一的测试失败是由于 scipy/numpy 版本兼容性问题，与 featuretools 代码无关。","time":{"start":1776097061744,"end":1776097061744}}]}
